        "action": "Make horse tethering on roads and pavements illegal",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "I want it to be a fineable/arrest-able offence if someone tethers a horse in a road or pavement as it can put the horse and other people at risk of possible accidents. Leaning horses in busy areas can also cause the horse distress.",
